{"tid":506531,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"大家認為香港應唔應該立騙婚罪？？","createTime":"2017-12-22T09:59:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-29T09:11:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"034e91c4e08009edcc3d8e0f31ad7642ec95fc36","tid":506531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T09:59:19.000Z","msg":"例如一個男人為咗錢扮鐘意一個女人然後同佢假結婚就係騙婚罪<br />\n<br />\n但一個女人為咗錢扮鐘意一個男人然後同佢假結婚就無事<br />\n<br />\n總之個騙婚罪就係女人可以攞晒著數而且無事，但男人做就係犯法要畀人拉"},{"pid":"fe01d61d3769be1254f454a63827a529c8c7d3e4","tid":506531,"uid":149978,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T10:10:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>例如一個男人為咗錢扮鐘意一個女人然後同佢假結婚就係騙婚罪<br />\n<br />\n但一個女人為咗錢扮鐘意一個男人然後同佢假結婚就無事<br />\n<br />\n總之個騙婚罪就係女人可以攞晒著數而且無事，但男人做就係犯法要畀人拉</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n女人為左錢，同男人結婚<br />\n都屬騙婚，要拉坐監"},{"pid":"19fa1b6f4d50bf6a6f15902cf2a9c190e5a7bc0c","tid":506531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:01:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a70b89660488c31385794a5f2aa91b503681b027","tid":506531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-22T11:47:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0c259c5bf3353e5a12d86e4c301ef4976e00055","tid":506531,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-29T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}